'''Fleet Technical Services''' or '''FTS''' were logistical support units attached to [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] [[Systems force|Systems Forces]]. They used mechanical specialists and technicians usually equipped in eight [[Evakmar-KDY transport]]s, each guarded by two [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|escort frigates]].

